data.description: Beautiful remodeled home with many upgrades and custom features.  Upgrades include new metal roof, new windows, new flooring. A cooks dream- Custom maple kitchen with maple dovetailed drawers, under cabinet lighting and corian countertops, black stainless appliances and island.  The inviting living room features an electric fireplace with stone and a hardwood mantel. The main bedroom features a custom closet system, shiplap wall, projector with 100' screen and a  sliding barn door.  The luxurious bath has a walk in tile shower with bluetooth speaker, a jetted tub and custom maple vanity with corian countertop.
